# Build-context excludes.
#
# The production target image (containers/agnostic/colab_prod/Dockerfile) is the
# only image that COPYs the whole repository, so keep host-specific and
# regenerated artifacts out of the context: they bloat the build, and host
# node_modules contains wrong-architecture native binaries (the production image
# rebuilds Linux-native deps with yarn/bundle).
#
# The existing dev/test/db/browser/moodle images only COPY specific files
# (their entrypoints, initDBs.sql, mise.toml), so these excludes do not affect
# them.
.git
.git/**
node_modules
**/node_modules
log
log/**
tmp
tmp/**
coverage
coverage/**
reports
reports/**
cucumber/**/reports
core.*
*.core
.yarn/install-state.gz
.byebug_history
